{"tid":216593,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"前曼聯球星跑倫敦馬拉松打撗離場","createTime":"2017-04-25T09:49:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-25T13:15:07.000Z","uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"881a284793c2e02262ac50693068598ec03541fd","tid":216593,"uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T09:49:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170425/large/1493106909_8b51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170425%2Flarge%2F1493106909_8b51.jpg&h=fd00a69a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n倫敦馬拉松雖然已經喺星期日已經跑咗，不過，餘波就日日都有，好似喺殘障組得第二嘅摩洛哥跑手艾哈迪，可能條短褲褲腳太闊，意外咁喺臨衝終點前露械，而呢個場面仲啱啱俾一名女觀眾拍底，女觀眾事後睇番部手機，都驚訝到擘大個口得個窿。另外，前曼聯球員科東尼亦有參與呢個賽事，不過，喺終點前600米就已經乏力，仲幾乎暈低，好彩有其他好心嘅跑手扶住佢完成賽事；而喺過終點之後，佢仲要立即上擔架床㖭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170425/large/1493106910_37df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170425%2Flarge%2F1493106910_37df.jpg&h=a14c28a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170425/large/1493106907_2df5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170425%2Flarge%2F1493106907_2df5.jpg&h=27c2f1a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170425/large/1493106906_d660.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170425%2Flarge%2F1493106906_d660.jpg&h=ed0c2625&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8820b6f17275682d8d334940ea6dc8e7917b1897","tid":216593,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T10:06:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c8c85c6cd5dada2d77bd60efafe6960d6653429c","tid":216593,"uid":40940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl